classDiagram
    title Chapter 11: LRU Cache Implementation
    
    class LRUCache~K, V~ {
        -capacity: usize
        -cache: HashMap~K, V~
        -order: VecDeque~K~
        +new(capacity) LRUCache
        +get(key) Option~&V~
        +put(key, value)
        +remove_lru() Option~V~
    }
    
    class HashMap~K, V~ {
        +insert()
        +get()
        +remove()
    }
    
    class VecDeque~K~ {
        +push_front()
        +pop_back()
        +remove()
    }
    
    LRUCache --> HashMap : uses for storage
    LRUCache --> VecDeque : uses for order
    
    Note over LRUCache: O(1) get/put\nEvicts least recently used
